      <content><![CDATA[<p>Note, that in the link to the detail page, we again add the parameter <code>?instancedate=${instancedate}</code>. Hence, we can use it in a detail formatter similarly as here in the display formatter.</p>
<div class="alert alert-info">Note that here we use a structure for a list as described for <a href="%(link0)">building lists with OpenCms 11</a>. You do not have to use display formatters and could also use <code>&lt;cms:search&gt;</code> instead of <code>&lt;cms:simplesearch&gt;</code>. E.g., when searching events in a <a href="%(link1)">full-text search</a>.</div>]]></content>
